        <abstract> 
<p>Has been invited to contribute geological instructions [to J. F. W. Herschel, ed., <hi rend="italic">Manual of scientific enquiry</hi> (1849); <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 1: 227–50]. Asks RO whether remarks on coral reefs appertain to geology rather than zoology.</p> 
            <p>Looks forward to visit by Owens.</p>
        </abstract>
